    "name": "Oathbound: Arena",
    "steam_appid": 2259400,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/bed1788ab474e3537a13c6323b786e80.poster.avif?t=1689352081\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/bed1788ab474e3537a13c6323b786e80.webm?t=1689352081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/bed1788ab474e3537a13c6323b786e80.mp4?t=1689352081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基于职业和团队机制的MMORPG</h2>Oathbound是一款采用Unreal Engine 5开发的MMORPG游戏，将传统的、石头剪刀布式的职业系统（例如《魔兽世界》）与回合制战斗（例如《巴尔德之门》）和可扩展的世界设计（例如《战记》）相结合。作为一个免费的独立版本，Oathbound：竞技场让玩家能够在重点放在PvE/PvP战斗和技能系统上的情况下体验游戏的主要特点，让玩家可以尝试不同的团队构成并练习，最终参加对阿卡亚的战斗。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/6a97acea1ff8b3ef7e425f09bc64dea0.poster.avif?t=1689352081\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/6a97acea1ff8b3ef7e425f09bc64dea0.webm?t=1689352081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/6a97acea1ff8b3ef7e425f09bc64dea0.mp4?t=1689352081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>MMORPG职业：选择具有独特技能的可玩职业。<br></li><li>团队管理：尝试不同的构建方式，以适应不同的玩法风格。 <br></li><li>在线多人游戏：在PvP/PvE战斗中脱颖而出，并与朋友一起组队作战。<br></li><li>多个竞技场：适应不同的环境，争夺战利品的同时调整策略。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/3e2385d20b4c19a097c9e5ac77d14d17.avif?t=1689352081\" width=600 height=194 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/c8930148641b1982dfcc37e782788fcd.poster.avif?t=1689352081\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/c8930148641b1982dfcc37e782788fcd.webm?t=1689352081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/c8930148641b1982dfcc37e782788fcd.mp4?t=1689352081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >回合制战术战斗</h2>Oathbound的战斗系统旨在鼓励玩家尝试不同的构建方式和对抗某些游戏策略。职业和反职业、技能和反技能都遵循石头剪刀布的设计，通过掌握游戏机制来获得游戏中的优势。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/0ec3635f265ae1ac19edaf48b1969e8c.avif?t=1689352081\" width=600 height=243 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/bdc94be294a88cd61a7969f03b88ecbe.poster.avif?t=1689352081\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/bdc94be294a88cd61a7969f03b88ecbe.webm?t=1689352081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/bdc94be294a88cd61a7969f03b88ecbe.mp4?t=1689352081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >交互式世界地图</h2> 以3D表示探索游戏世界，并发现可点击的元素，如房屋或古老的遗迹。自然边界以沉浸式的方式限制了可访问的地图部分。点击兴趣点可以进入专用的小型3D地图。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/5f07387da46dd2ced569aff4e243ec6c.poster.avif?t=1689352081\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/5f07387da46dd2ced569aff4e243ec6c.webm?t=1689352081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/5f07387da46dd2ced569aff4e243ec6c.mp4?t=1689352081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可探索的生物群系</h2> 以第三人称视角探索游戏世界的专用区域。在不同大小的有限兴趣点地图中收集资源，与其他玩家互动或进行交易。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/729b5223fb0991b71829a414c4e8e28f.poster.avif?t=1689352081\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/729b5223fb0991b71829a414c4e8e28f.webm?t=1689352081\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/729b5223fb0991b71829a414c4e8e28f.mp4?t=1689352081\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >加入Oathbound社区</h2> Oathbound和Oathbound: Arena的开发与社区进行密切而透明的交流。玩家测试和提前体验也会被纳入开发路线图中。加入社区，成为其中的一员！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2259400/extras/4867142ac04ca90227c2f9f26fe0fa84.avif?t=1689352081\" width=600 height=243 /></span><br>",
